title: Jason La Canfora on NFL Week 1 overreactions (Football 09/12)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to break down some of the biggest overreactions from Week 1 of the 2018 NFL season. Are the Ravens and Bengals better than the Steelers? Patrick Mahomes for MVP??? Are the Jets an AFC Wild Card contender? Could the Raiders cut Derek Carr after the season? All those questions answered plus much more.
